host.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=80&amp;promocode=laborday1155\">Direct order link</a>.</p><ul><li>256MB guaranteed/512MB burstable memory</li><li>25GB storage</li><li>500GB/month data transfer</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Their \u201cBeginner\u201d plan would be $6.75/month after the discount with 512MB/1024MB memory, 30GB storage and 750GB/month data transfer. It takes PayPal, credit card, Google Checkout and <em>Mail In Payment</em> \u2014 don\u2019t expect instant setup on that though. Servers in New York City with WeLinkNYC (test IP: 204.145.80.237). Domain has been registered since 2004. Ernie is 25/26, and HV Host is a registered in NY.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudson-valley-host-4-05-256mb-openvz-vps-in-nyc-labor-day-sale%2F&amp;t=Hudson%20Valley%20Host%20-%20%244.05%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20NYC%20Labor%20Day%20Sale\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Hudson%20Valley%20Host%20-%20%244.05%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20NYC%20Labor%20Day%20Sale&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudson-valley-host-4-05-256mb-openvz-vps-in-nyc-labor-day-sale%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label